.services-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
gap: 2rem;
margin: 2rem 0;
}

.service-card {
background: #ffffff;
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 2rem;
box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
transition: all 0.3s ease;
border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
height: 100%;
}

.service-card:hover {
transform: translateY(-5px);
box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
border-color: #8a63d2;
}

.service-icon {
width: 64px;
height: 64px;
border-radius: 12px;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8a63d2 0%, #5e35b1 100%);
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
color: white;
}

.service-card h3 {
color: #2d1b69;
margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.service-card p {
color: #495057;
line-height: 1.6;
margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
flex-grow: 1;
}

.service-link {
color: #8a63d2;
text-decoration: none;
font-weight: 600;
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.service-link:hover {
color: #5e35b1;
transform: translateX(5px);
}

.service-link::after {
content: '‚Üí';
margin-left: 0.5rem;
transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.service-link:hover::after {
transform: translateX(5px);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
.services-grid {
grid-template-columns: 1fr;
}

.service-card {
padding: 1.5rem;
}
}

Bizning Xizmatlarimiz

Obsidian Asosidagi Veb-saytlar
Bilimingizni chiroyli va funksional veb-saytga aylantiring. Hujjatlar, vikilar va shaxsiy bilimlarni boshqarish uchun ajoyib yechim.
Batafsil ‚Üí

To'liq Stack Dasturlash
G'oyadan tortib ishga tushirishgacha bo'lgan barcha bosqichlarni o'z ichiga olgan veb-dasturlash xizmatlari. Sizning ehtiyojlaringizga moslashtirilgan, moslashuvchan va yuqori samaradorlikdagi veb-ilovalar yaratamiz.
Batafsil ‚Üí

Telegram Bot Yaratish
Ishlarni avtomatlashtirish, foydalanuvchilar bilan muloqotni osonlashtirish va biznes jarayonlarini takomillashtirish uchun moslashtirilgan Telegram botlari. Oddiy chatbotlardan tortib murakkab biznes yechimlarigacha.
Batafsil ‚Üí

Sun'iy Intellekt va Avtomatlashtirish
Biznesingiz samaradorligini oshirish uchun sun'iy intellekt va avtomatlashtirish kuchidan foydalaning. Biz eng yangi AI yechimlarini integratsiya qilamiz.
Batafsil ‚Üí

Mikroservislar
Biznesingiz bilan birga rivojlanadigan mikroservislar arxitekturasi. Mustaqil ishlaydigan, mustahkam va o'zaro muvofiqlashgan xizmatlar yaratamiz.
Batafsil ‚Üí

